e in both\nsimulations and observations, including a Hitomi re-flight and\ncalorimeter-based instruments with higher spatial resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 May 2017 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Sep 2017 14:31:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-08"}
