 percent lower than those of\nthe Vestoids; however, identification and compositional analysis of additional\nouter belt basaltic asteroids would help to confirm or refute this result.\nGiven the gradient in oxidation state which existed within the solar nebula,\nthese results tentatively suggest that these objects formed at either a\ndifferent time or location than 4 Vesta.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 May 2017 18:29:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-19"}
