per, we give a characterization of initial\nconfigurations from which the robots without chirality can form a plane and a\nnew plane formation algorithm for solvable instances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2017 11:06:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 May 2017 06:14:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-22"}
