red Ni$_{1-x}$Pt$_x$ (0.4$<$ x $<$0.6) binary alloys. Our\ntheoretical predictions agree more than reasonably well with both earlier\nexperimental as well as theoretical investigations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2017 12:25:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 May 2017 13:03:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-12"}
