precise production of lithium-ion battery electrode\nmaterials, enhancing the overall battery cycle efficiency and charging speed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2017 15:27:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-19"}
